To End All Wars;;2001;;R;;Action,Drama,War;;7.0;;David L. Cunningham;;Robert Carlyle,Kiefer Sutherland,Ciarán McMenamin,Mark Strong,Yûgo Sasô,Sakae Kimura,James Cosmo,Masayuki Yui,John Gregg,Shû Nakajima,Greg Ellis,Pip Torrens,James McCarthy,Brendan Cowell,Winton Nicholson,Tracy Anderson,Duff Armour,Robert Jobe;;A true story about four Allied POWs who endure harsh treatment from their Japanese captors during World War II while being forced to build a railroad through the Burmese jungle. Ultimately they find true freedom by forgiving their enemies. Based on the true story of Ernest Gordon.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0243609/